tes. In addition, particles larger than a couple of\nmicrons are not significantly perturbed by solar radiation pressure in the\nenvironment around Arrokoth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Mar 2022 01:56:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
