\nlong baseline experiments: DUNE, T2HK, and T2HKK, at a confidence level of\n$5\\sigma$. From the result it is clear that, our model can be tested in its\n$3\\sigma$ C.L. with $5\\sigma$ allowed region of DUNE, T2HK and T2HKK.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Mar 2022 07:26:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 May 2023 15:37:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-23"}
