hers to better understand\nsmart contract vulnerabilities by defining various dimensions of the problem\nand supporting our classification with mappings with literature-based\nclassifications and frequency distributions of the defined categories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Mar 2022 15:42:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
